high_descs: Go to the counter to the left of the fridge.
Take the knife from the counter.
Turn right, go forward, at the fridge turn right, go forward to the left side of the sink.
Cut the apple in the sink into pieces.
Turn around go forward to the fridge.
Put the knife on the bottom shelf of the fridge.
Turn around, go back to the sink with the apple.
Take a piece of apple from the sink.
Go forward and to the left to the counter space to the right of the coffee machine in the left corner.
Put the apple piece on the blue plate on the counter.
Take the plate from the counter.
Turn right, go forward, turn left at the fridge.
Put the plate on the left side of the bottom shelf of the fridge.
